com.msd.queryengine

Class CommitteeWhereClauseBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.msd.queryengine.CommitteeWhereClauseBuilder

  • public class CommitteeWhereClauseBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    CommitteeWhereClauseBuilder builds the where clause required to filter the search results in the main page based on different parameters associated with committee data like served before/not, specific conference or journal committee served

      • createCommitteeWhereClause

        public void createCommitteeWhereClause(SearchParameters searchParams)
        Builds the where clause for committee based on user search criteria such as served previously or not specific served years, or specific conference/journal committees served. Accumulates the built where clause into where clause built so far.
        Parameters:
        searchParams - The user input Search parameters based on which the where clause is built
